gate: OPEN
task: S74-TB1
title: Identify Track Get API Calls in Object History
description: |
  Locate all track/get API calls being made from the object history screen:
  - Find where https://localhost:5173/api/ws/track/get is being called
  - Identify the components or hooks triggering these calls
  - Document how the daily endpoint is already providing the same data
  - Map the data flow from daily endpoint to UI components

acceptance:
  - List all locations where track/get API is called in history
  - Document data mapping between daily endpoint and UI needs
  - Confirm daily endpoint provides all required data
  - Identify any redundant data processing

requires: []
estimated: 2 hours
